### IntelliJ HTTP Client - Exchange Rate APIs
### 사용법:
### 1) 우측 상단에서 환경을 dev로 선택
### 2) 인증키는 http/http-client.private.env.json 에서 로드

@localBaseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@eximBaseUrl = https://oapi.koreaexim.go.kr
@eximLatestRatePath = /site/program/financial/exchangeJSON
@searchDate = 20260429

### ========================================
### 1) 한국수출입은행 환율 조회 (원본 응답 확인)
### ========================================
GET {{eximBaseUrl}}{{eximLatestRatePath}}?authkey={{eximAuthKey}}&searchdate={{searchDate}}&data=AP01
Accept: application/json

### ========================================
### 2) 로컬 - 전체 통화 최신 환율 조회
### ========================================
GET {{localBaseUrl}}/exchange-rate/latest
Accept: application/json

### ========================================
### 3) 로컬 - 특정 통화 최신 환율 조회 (USD)
### ========================================
GET {{localBaseUrl}}/exchange-rate/latest/USD
Accept: application/json

### ========================================
### 4) 로컬 - 특정 통화 최신 환율 조회 (KRW, 실패 케이스 확인)
### ========================================
GET {{localBaseUrl}}/exchange-rate/latest/KRW
Accept: application/json

### ========================================
### 5) 로컬 - 주문 생성 (KRW -> USD)
### ========================================
POST {{localBaseUrl}}/order
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "fromCurrency": "KRW",
  "toCurrency": "USD",
  "forexAmount": 100
}

### ========================================
### 6) 로컬 - 주문 생성 (USD -> KRW)
### ========================================
POST {{localBaseUrl}}/order
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "fromCurrency": "USD",
  "toCurrency": "KRW",
  "forexAmount": 100
}

### ========================================
### 7) 로컬 - 주문 목록 조회
### ========================================
GET {{localBaseUrl}}/order/list
Accept: application/json
